com.esri.mo2.ui.toc
Class TreeTocPopupActions

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.ui.cmn.Actions
        |
        +--com.esri.mo2.ui.toc.TreeTocPopupActions
public class TreeTocPopupActions
extends Actions

TocPopupActions is a collection of default actions for TocPopup menu. An action can be accessed and reused by its ID defined in the TocPopup class.
